    <string name="introduction_dialog_title">Introduction</string>
    <string name="introduction_dialog_message">
        Welcome to Wireless Control!\n
        \n
        This app is designed to manage your Wifi (and more soon!) while you\'re moving about.\n
        \n
        Set up some geofences on areas where you normally have Wifi and
        Wireless Control will toggle your Wifi on/off for you when you enter or leave that area automatically!\n
        \n
        This will stop your Wifi from constantly looking for new networks and in turn, save some battery.\n
        \n
        Note: App is still in beta and under development.\n
        \n
        If you spot any issues or have a feature in mind, please write a review!\n
        \n
    </string>
